msgctxt "sn36.26:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 36 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 36 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn36.26:0.2"
msgid "3. Aṭṭhasatapariyāyavagga "
msgstr "3. The Explanation of the Hundred and Eight "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 26. Sambahulabhikkhusutta → bhikkhunā (pts1)
msgctxt "sn36.26:0.3"
msgid "26. Sambahulabhikkhusutta "
msgstr "26. With Several Mendicants "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn36.26:1.1"
msgid "Atha kho sambahulā bhikkhū yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkamiṃsu; upasaṅkamitvā … pe … ekamantaṃ nisinnā kho te bhikkhū bhagavantaṃ etadavocuṃ: "
msgstr "Then several mendicants went up to the Buddha, bowed, sat down to one side, and said to him: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn36.26:1.2"
msgid "“katamā nu kho, bhante, vedanā, katamo vedanāsamudayo, katamā vedanāsamudayagāminī paṭipadā? "
msgstr "“Sir, what is feeling? What’s the origin of feeling? What’s the practice that leads to the origin of feeling? "

msgctxt "sn36.26:1.3"
msgid "Katamo vedanānirodho, katamā vedanānirodhagāminī paṭipadā? "
msgstr "What’s the cessation of feeling? What’s the practice that leads to the cessation of feeling? "

msgctxt "sn36.26:1.4"
msgid "Ko vedanāya assādo, ko ādīnavo, kiṃ nissaraṇan”ti? "
msgstr "And what is feeling’s gratification, drawback, and escape?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn36.26:1.5"
msgid "“Tisso imā, bhikkhave, vedanā—"
msgstr "“Mendicants, there are these three feelings. "

msgctxt "sn36.26:1.6"
msgid "sukhā vedanā, dukkhā vedanā, adukkhamasukhā vedanā. "
msgstr "pleasant, painful, and neutral. "

msgctxt "sn36.26:1.7"
msgid "Imā vuccanti, bhikkhave, vedanā. "
msgstr "These are called feeling. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn36.26:1.8"
msgid "Phassasamudayā vedanāsamudayo. "
msgstr "Feeling originates from contact. "

msgctxt "sn36.26:1.9"
msgid "Taṇhā vedanāsamudayagāminī paṭipadā. "
msgstr "Craving is the practice that leads to the origin of feeling. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn36.26:1.10"
msgid "Phassanirodhā … pe … "
msgstr "When contact ceases, feeling ceases. … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn36.26:1.11"
msgid "yo vedanāya chandarāgavinayo chandarāgappahānaṃ. Idaṃ vedanāya nissaraṇan”ti. "
msgstr "Removing and giving up desire and greed for feeling: this is its escape.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn36.26:1.12"
msgid "Chaṭṭhaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
